name: Bat Style Tower Rack
description:
If you want quality, reliability and style then look no further then FreeRange Wakeboarding. Buy from a brand you can trust.
 
This Bat Style FreeRange Wakeboarding Tower Rack combines style with functionality, keeping your deck clear of boards whilst looking the part with the high quality polished finish.
 
-          Tower rack is made from high quality aluminium and polished to a mirror finish.
-          Tower rack can fit both 2.5” and 2.25” towers. Rubber spacers are provided for both sizes, and protect your tower from scratches.
-          Designed to fit 2 wakeboards or wakeskates
-          High quality angle adjustable mounting bracket with 4 bolt design.
 
Items included:
-          1 Bat Style Tower rack in polished aluminium
-          1 Bracket to fit your 2.5” or 2.25” wakeboard tower. Brackets are adjustable allowing for custom installation on any tower
-          Rubber spacers/protectors for 2.5” and 2.25” towers
 
** Please note: Wakeboard is not included with this product.

name: Bimini Rack Stainless Steel
description:
If you want quality, reliability and style then look no further then FreeRange Wakeboarding Bimini Racks. Buy from a brand you can trust with a proven track record.

These racks have a unique design as they sit on top of your existing bimini cover (can also be fitted to tower bimini’s), which is great to get boards and skis off the deck.

- Constructed with high quality 6060 aluminium tube.
- Custom made marine grade 316 polished Stainless Steel fittings.
- Heavy duty protection foam keeps your boards safe from damage.
- 100% UV stable sleeves keeps the protection foam from degradation caused by sunlight.
- FreeRange logo on the front two sleeves.
- With a total length of 1050mm these racks will fit most bimini covers.
- Custom lengths available upon request.
- Fitting is as easy as riveting the racks onto your bimini frame.  Stainless Steel Rivets included.
- Next business day dispatch ensures fast delivery.

Please note bimini cover, wakeboards, and skis are not provided.  Pickup is available from Melbourne, Victoria. International buyers, please contact us with post/zipcode and country for quote of shipping costs. 

Checkout with the safety and security of PAYPAL!
